title: In Ghost House Inn
subTitle: Thomas Kutty buys a haunted bungalow and convinces his friends to stay with him on the first night. The trouble begins when they actually see the ghost of the mistress who was killed 70 years ago.

title: Idukki Gold
subTitle: Michael returns to India and puts out an advertisement to try and find his old friends. Soon, he meets Ravi and Madan and together they set off on a road trip to meet the others.

title: Seelabathi
subTitle: Seelabhati along with her mother visits a remote village where she starts working as a computer teacher. When some students mysteriously disappear, the villagers start blaming her educational course.

title: Udayon
subTitle: Kunju is so obsessed with his land that he even grabs his sister's share by forging his father's will. Though he is known to be stubborn, his love for agriculture is appreciated by his youngest son.

title: Ananthabhadram
subTitle: To honour his mother's final wish, Ananthan attempts to light a lamp at the family temple. However, his quest is thwarted by an evil magician who seeks to harness the temple's hidden powers.

title: Minnal Murali
subTitle: Jaison, a young tailor, gains superpowers after being struck by lightning. However, he must thwart the evil intentions of an unexpected adversary to become the superhero that his rural village needs.

title: Hridayam
subTitle: Arun, a young man, enrols in an engineering college but falls prey to bad habits. As he grows up, he decides to turn over a new leaf and become a responsible adult.

title: Oru Maravathoor Kanavu
subTitle: Michael and his family buy a farm that is coveted by a rich man, who makes life difficult for him. Thereafter, Michael's brother, Chandy, comes to support him.

title: Two Countries
subTitle: Ullas schemes to marry Simran, woman with a disability, to avoid repaying a debt, but faces complications when Laya, a wealthy alcoholic, enters his life, turning his plans upside down.

title: Lollipop
subTitle: Franco, who runs an automobile workshop, and his sister Jenny, a college student, share a very strong bond. Matters take a turn when Franco falls in love with Jenny's enemy.

title: Lollipop
subTitle: Franco, who runs an automobile workshop, and his sister Jenny, a college student, share a very strong bond. Matters take a turn when Franco falls in love with Jenny's enemy.

title: Vishudhan
subTitle: Sunny, a priest, comes to know that Vavachan is running an old age home with vile intentions. He wants the corpses of the inmates for the medical college run by his son and Sunny wants to expose him.

title: Sullu
subTitle: Jithu, a carefree boy, gets trapped in an abandoned house, forcing him to reflect on his life and appreciate what he once took for granted.

title: Sarkkar Colony
subTitle: Life in a modest government colony takes a turn as its residents pursue a side venture, hoping to ease financial burdens but ending up in unexpected chaos.

title: Classmates
subTitle: A group of college friends meet after many years for a class reunion. However, due to some unexpected turn of events, several dark secrets are revealed, which changes their lives.

title: Rasathanthram
subTitle: Premachandran, a carpenter, rescues Kanmani, an ill-treated maid, and takes her into his care. However, to escape from her former abusers, Kanmani dresses up as a boy and joins the team of carpenters.

title: Aadu 2
subTitle: Shaji Pappan and his team participate in a tug-of-war tournament to overcome their financial crisis. However, fate entangles them in a counterfeiting deal.

title: Puthiyamugham
subTitle: An honest fresher faces chaos in his life by some boys as he joined collge. After years of sufferings, he finally decides to take on them.

title: Bro Daddy
subTitle: Two close friends, John and Kurian, wish to take their friendship one step further and get their children married. However, they are unaware of the lives their children lead in the city.

title: Baba Kalyani
subTitle: Baba Kalyani, a police officer, travels to Kochi to uncover a terrorist conspiracy. He must not only work on the case but also deal with old rivals who are hell-bent on settling scores with him.

title: Baba Kalyani
subTitle: Baba Kalyani, a police officer, travels to Kochi to uncover a terrorist conspiracy. He must not only work on the case but also deal with old rivals who are hell-bent on settling scores with him.

title: Again Kasargod Khader Bhai
subTitle: Kasim Bhai is found murdered. The suspicion falls on the Kaladarshana team and the unfolding of the murder mystery forms the rest of the story.

title: Cheriya Kallanum Valiya Poleesum
subTitle: Sadasivan comes across a house where the owner, Kumaran, has committed suicide to protect his wife, Soumini. However, what is even stranger is that a man who is visually challenged is always around.

title: Pachuvum Kovalanum
subTitle: For TV director Thomaskutty Pachu, nothing is more stressful than dealing with his pesky cousin Joseph Kovalan. That is, until a murder occurs on the set.

title: Ohm Shanthi Oshaana
subTitle: Pooja Mathew, a spirited young girl, dreams about marrying only for love. Thus, she stops at nothing to impress Giri, who saved her once from a group of unruly men.

title: Evidam Swargamanu
subTitle: Mathews owns a farm that is the envy of everyone in the village. It attracts the attention of a dirty land dealer, who entangles him in a vicious bureaucratic web to take it away from him.

title: Ring Master
subTitle: Prince, a dog trainer, faces an awkward situation when his pet dog Diana acts in a film alongside his former lover, an actress who shares the same name as the dog.

title: Oru Marubhoomikkadha
subTitle: Madhavan is an honest and hardworking man. However, when a rich man's daughter, Eliana, asks him to abduct her and demand a ransom from her father, his life turns upside down.

title: Guruvayur Ambalanadayil
subTitle: A young man eagerly awaits his wedding, but fate twists cruelly, forcing him into a lifelong bond with a woman who harbours nothing but resentment for him.

title: Lucifer
subTitle: The demise of the leader of a political party leads to a massive power struggle. Amidst the chaos, a mystical man named Stephen comes in to ascend the throne.
